 wings go swoosh? "}]},{"type":"element","name":"rac_hilight_teacher_inst_new","elements":[{"type":"text","text":"Review "},{"type":"element","name":"rac_highlight_teacher_inst_Italic","elements":[{"type":"text","text":"wings"}]},{"type":"text","text":" Vocabulary Card.  "}]},{"type":"element","name":"rac_d-hed_page_number","elements":[{"type":"text","text":"Car "}]},{"type":"element","name":"rac_teacher-talk_blue","elements":[{"type":"text","text":"Does a car make any sounds other than the horn? What does a car sound like? What shapes would you use to make a car? "}]},{"type":"element","name":"rac_d-hed_page_number","elements":[{"type":"text","text":"Boat "}]},{"type":"element","name":"rac_teacher-talk_blue","elements":[{"type":"text","text":"What is different about a boat and other vehicles we read about? How do you move the oar to row a boat? "}]},{"type":"element","name":"rac_d-hed_page_number","elements":[{"type":"text","text":"Train "}]},{"type":"element","name":"rac_teacher-talk_blue","elements":[{"type":"text","text":"The engine chugs as the train moves. What other noises do trains make? What shapes can you find on the train? "}]},{"type":"element","name":"rac_hilight_teacher_inst_new","elements":[{"type":"text","text":"Review "},{"type":"element","name":"rac_highlight_teacher_inst_Italic","elements":[{"type":"text","text":"engine"}]},{"type":"text","text":" Vocabulary Card. "}]},{"type":"element","name":"rac_d-hed_page_number","elements":[{"type":"text","text":"Digger "}]},{"type":"element","name":"rac_teacher-talk_blue","elements":[{"type":"text","text":"What shapes could you use to build diggers? How do they move?  "}]}]},{"type":"element","name":"section","elements":[{"type":"element","name":"rac_column_heds_with_rule","elements":[{"type":"text","text":"Extended Play "}]},{"type":"element","name":"rac_body-text","elements":[{"type":"text","text":"Provide found objects (buttons, paper plates, paper towel tubes, etc) and various-sized cut out shapes, along